uiEntry.title: root
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

uiEntry.title: top
uiEntry.script: function UpdateSlider() local value = Component.GetProperty("Parent.Value") - Component.GetProperty("stepSize") Component.SetProperty("Parent.Value", value) Component.Call("Parent.LuaCall", "Update") end

uiEntry.title: bottom
uiEntry.script: function UpdateSlider() local value = Component.GetProperty("Parent.Value") + Component.GetProperty("stepSize") Component.SetProperty("Parent.Value", value) Component.Call("Parent.LuaCall", "Update") end

uiEntry.title: row_example
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address) local panel = UIComponent(this:Parent("load_replay"))
function OnSelect() panel:LuaCall("Selected", Address) end
function OnDblClick() panel:LuaCall("OnAccept") end
function Select(s) if s then this:SetState("selected") OnSelect() else this:SetState("unselected") end end
